\h ACRONYMS \d

During your adventures, you may encounter various acronyms. Here is a guide to what they mean.
Note that the use of acronyms in IC communication is prohibited! (What's "IC"? See below!)

AFK     Away From Keyboard`

BRB     Be Right Back`

IC      In Character
        Something said or done in the context of role-playing.

INPC    Interactive Non-Player Character
        A character that is usually controlled by the game server, and sometimes controlled, or otherwise managed, by staff.

IRL     In Real Life`

MUD     Multi-User Dungeon`

NPC     Non-Player Character
        A character controlled by the game server.

OOC     Out Of Character
        Something said or done as a player, outside the context of role-playing.

PC      Player Character
        A character controlled by a human player.

PK      Player Kill
        The act of attacking another PC.

RP      Role-Playing`

